Business WiFi, Fibre & connectivity services

   We create intuitive, efficient and secure connection spaces

1st very high speed WiFi platform

   A telecom operator since 2002, Wifirst is the French leader in managed
   Wi-Fi on the Hospitality & Residences markets. Wifirst is committed to
   continuous innovation to offer a network capable of absorbing the
   spectacular rise in Internet usage, offering high value-added services
   and making WiFi the technical base for the digital transformation of
   its customers.

   About Wifirst      WiFi as a Service

Our connectivity services

   Wifirst supports all professionals on all their connectivity projects:
   WiFi, fiber optic, TV, Cast, VoIP. True operator declared to ARCEP and
   pioneer of WiFi as a Service, Wifirst takes absolutely everything in
   charge, you do not have to worry about the management of your network.

   Discover our solutions
   Connectivity services : business WiFi, fiber optic, IPTV
   Best WiFi expertise

Unparalleled technical expertise

   The technical expertise is in Wifirst's DNA since its inception. We
   realized early on that the quality of the connection experience was
   going to be the key to our development. The technical teams have
   therefore invested over the years to offer innovative technologies that
   are constantly evolving.

   Discover our technologies

Vertical solutions

   We support all professionals in the digitalization of their
   establishments.
   Hotel WiFi systems
   Hospitality
   An essential technical update for all hotels
   Camping WiFi systems
   Campings
   A WiFi & Fibre solution for all players in outdoor hospitality
   WiFi in student accommodation
   Student accommodation
   Leader of Internet access in student accommodation
   Managed WiFi solutions for senior living
   Senior housing
   Connectivity made simple for senior living residents
   Room-Area-Network-wide

A connection experience like at home

   We often hear about the concept of customer experience "as at home". In
   terms of connectivity, the idea is to offer each customer a private
   WiFi network on which he can connect simply, and safely, all his
   personal equipment. This solution, which we call the "Room Area
   Network" is also the one that allows us to offer our Chromecast "Stream
   & Cast" offers.

   Room Area Network       Stream & Cast

The evolution of uses

   Thanks to our core network, all traffic is centralized in our
   datacenters and we see every day the exceptional share of video
   streaming in the Internet. In particular, we have been connecting
   students since 2002 and we have been witnessing a profound
   transformation in the way consumption programs are used.

   Learn more
   Uses of the internet

